\mu
\mathbb{R}
A
\mu
[a,b]
h
\frac{1}{2h}\int_a^b\mu(A\cap(x-h,x+h))\,\text{d}x\le \mu(A).
 \frac1{2h}\,\int_{[a,b]}\mu(A\cap(x-h,x+h))\,dx=\frac1{2h}\,\int_{[a,b]}\int_{(x-h,x+h)}\,1_A(t)\,d\mu(t)\,dx\\ \leq\frac1{2h}\int_{(a-h,b+h)}\int_{[t-h,t+h]}\,1_A(t)\,dx\,d\mu(t)=\int_{(a-h,b+h)}\,1_A(t)\,d\mu(t)=\mu(A\cap(a-h,b+h))=\mu(A). 
